Author: cinnamonbicycle
Text: I can tell you from experience that it doesn't stop. You'll only get worse. I know it's impossible to eat maintenance. I know it's impossible to make yourself care. But if you don't do *something*, you will reach a point of no return. Please, ask for help. I can tell this isn't what you want for yourself. Consider going to treatment where the responsibility of feeding yourself will be off your shoulders. You can get out of this. It doesn't feel like it now, but you really can.
